25/01/2010
TIRANA, Albania -- Police at the biggest port in country, Durres, arrested two people allegedly carrying 15kg of marijuana on Sunday (January 24th). Authorities got a tip over the phone that the pair had drugs hidden in their car, destined for Italy. Police are trying to determine if a drug trafficking network is involved. (Ora News, Shekulli, Balkan Web - 24/01/10)
